From: Venkat <venkat@blustream.in>
Date: Sat, 21 Mar 2026 05:36:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: project-aware Integrity Console

- AuditView: category selector uses ProjectStore categories, shows PROJECT MODE badge
- IntegrityConsolePanel: V4 check probes IndexedDB in project mode (store counts, corpus health, strategy output)
- IntegrityConsolePanel: Rebuild clears IndexedDB corpus/outputs for project categories
- IntegrityConsolePanel: Target display shows [PROJECT] tag and resolves category name from ProjectStore
- SignalCorpusPanel: reads corpus from IndexedDB in project mode, shows IndexedDB badge
- SignalCorpusPanel: category dropdown uses project categories
- All legacy Firestore paths preserved for CORE_CATEGORIES mode
---
